Pernambuco Championship 1924

Source: "Campeonato Pernambucano - 1915 a 1970", book written by 
Carlos Celso Cordeiro and Luciano Guedes Cordeiro.
13/04/24     Sport Recife 9-0 Equador-PE
13/04/24     Santa Cruz 4-1 CS Peres
27/04/24     América-PE 3-2 Náutico
27/04/24     Torre 2-1 Flamengo (RE)
04/05/24     Sport Recife 3-1 Santa Cruz
04/05/24     Equador-PE 3-0 CS Peres
11/05/24     Flamengo (RE) 3-1 América-PE
11/05/24     Náutico - Equador-PE   [Náutico won by W.O.]
[Equador was excluded from the competition; his remaining matches,
against Flamengo, Santa Cruz, América and Torre were awarded as lost
by W.O.]
13/05/24        Santa Cruz 1-0 Torre
13/05/24        Sport Recife 3-0 CS Peres
18/05/24        Flamengo (RE) 5-2 Náutico
25/05/24        Sport Recife 3-1 América-PE
25/05/24        Náutico 8-0 CS Peres
