06/07/24        Torre 2-0 CS Peres
13/07/24        Sport Recife 5-2 Flamengo (RE)
20/07/24        Santa Cruz 6-1 América-PE
27/07/24        Flamengo (RE) 7-0 CS Peres
03/08/24        Sport Recife 3-1 Flamengo (RE)
03/08/24        América-PE 4-0 Torre
10/08/24        América-PE 4-2 Santa Cruz
10/08/24        Náutico 2-1 CS Peres
17/08/24        Torre 2-2 Flamengo (RE)
17/08/24        Sport Recife - CS Peres   [Sport won by W.O.]
24/08/24        Santa Cruz 4-1 Náutico
24/08/24        América-PE 2-1 Flamengo (RE)
31/08/24        Sport Recife 3-3 Torre
31/08/24        Santa Cruz - CS Peres   [Santa Cruz won by W.O.]
[Peres abandoned the competition; his remaining matches, against América,
Torre and Flamengo were awarded as lost by W.O.]
